{"data":[{"date":"04:09 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.\r\n</h2><h2>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video data-dashjs-player=\"\" src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/201806/273029/stream.mpd\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Caballero<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ed1n ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Iceland, nh\u01b0ng Willy Caballero v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 Sampaoli tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 sang 3 trung v\u1ec7, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Argentina \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. Caballero, trong \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vui l\u00f2ng, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi anh c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 c\u0103m ph\u1eabn. Ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Caballero ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho&hellip; Rebic ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0, khi\u1ebfn th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 36 tu\u1ed5i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i &ldquo;s\u1edf th\u00edch&rdquo; chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1. \u1ede m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u01b0 World Cup, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea1m nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ngu ng\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Caballero.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Caballero tiep tuc lam tro he trong khung go\" title=\"Caballero ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 trong khung g\u1ed7\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/willy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Caballero ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 trong khung g\u1ed7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Argentina s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 qu\u00e1 nhanh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi th\u1ebf th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Iceland, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m nay thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n. Trong hi\u1ec7p 1, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh tr\u1ed1ng (Perez b\u1ecf l\u1ee1), v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7, Argentina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc, m\u00e0&hellip; bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, khi\u1ebfn Caballero tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu Rakitic c\u1ee7a Croatia d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thua 0-3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina\" title=\"Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/argen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Argentina s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Sampaoli \u0111ang ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iceland b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u 1 ng\u00e0y, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Argentina tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. \u00d4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, m\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3: Argentina b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi gi\u1eef b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh HLV n\u00e0y th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn&hellip; kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, \u00f4ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi xoay sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u00fd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 y\u1ebfu nay c\u00f2n y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n, trong khi h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, Sampaoli \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea3 Dybala l\u1eabn Higuain v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u00f2 tr\u1ed1ng g\u00ec. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111ang m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Argentina s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sampaoli\" title=\"Sampaoli\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/sam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia: S\u1ef1 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Sampaoli</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>V\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho Croatia<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh c\u1ee7a Dalic, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1, trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca-ro ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n t\u1ed1i \u0111a m\u1ed1i nguy n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, trong khi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n Ivan Rakitic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3, khi c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang. Luka Modric khi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 n\u1ee9c l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, trong khi Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed 2-3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Croatia c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Argentina.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina gi\u00fap \u0110T Croatia gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Leo Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u00e1n t\u1eed, khi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u mong Iceland kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, m\u1edbi c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Argentina 0-3 Croatia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina 0-3 Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Thong-so-Argentina.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina 0-3 Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang hien tai cua bang D World Cup 2018\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/tram.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-argentina-vs-croatia-463-189188.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ket-qua-argentina-vs-croatia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-argentina-vs-croatia-463-189188.html\">Argentina 0-3 Croatia (KT): Messi m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Albiceleste thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Lionel Messi l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n k\u00e9m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Iceland, \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c. Tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina-465-189201.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina-465-189201.html\">Luka Modric: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f4 l\u1eadp Messi, kh\u00f4ng cho anh ta nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng</span><br>\r\nTrong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00f4 l\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng cho Lionel Messi nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"435","checkdouble":"189200"},{"date":"04:03 22/06","title":"Luka Modric: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f4 l\u1eadp Messi, kh\u00f4ng cho anh ta nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00f4 l\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng cho Lionel Messi nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd khi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e9p ch\u1eb7t khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Croatia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhanh t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean r\u1ed3i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e9t v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 ba h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Willy Caballero gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Luka Modric v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat xa hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1eadp ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Argentina, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Rakitic ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina: &quot;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y nh\u00ecn th\u00ec \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. \u0110\u00fang, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f4 l\u1eadp Messi, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng. Ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft Messi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 3-0 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Sau hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Davor Suker t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong, Modric c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i: &quot;M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn, ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Croatia t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;D\u00f9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng Croatia kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u1ed9i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Croatia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Iceland v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-argentina-vs-croatia-463-189188.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ket-qua-argentina-vs-croatia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-argentina-vs-croatia-463-189188.html\">Argentina 0-3 Croatia (KT): Messi m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Albiceleste thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Lionel Messi l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n k\u00e9m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Iceland, \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c. Tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"434","checkdouble":"189201"},{"date":"04:25 22/06","title":"Jorge Sampaoli: \"Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Messi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i World Cup. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, khi Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nArgentina tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi cho thi\u00ean h\u1ea1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng d\u00f9 Albiceleste ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ebfm ai ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Rebic, Modric v\u00e0 Rakitic \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm Argentina trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia, t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@GaryLineker: </strong></em>&ldquo;M\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Croatia, nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1eebng \u1ea5y n\u0103m theo d\u00f5i \u0110T Argentina thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u00f4i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecd t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/me.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi v\u00e0 Argentina ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<em><strong><br>\r\n@Jermainejunior:</strong></em><strong> </strong>&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i cho Messi, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau Copa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@WelBeast:</strong></em><strong> </strong>&ldquo;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho Sampaoli v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean anh ta \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Iceland. N\u1ebfu qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Argentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<em>&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@katienolan:</strong></em> &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n cho Salah c\u1ee7a Argentina.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@MiguelDelaney: </strong></em>&ldquo;Messi r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Khi b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y quay l\u1ea1i \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Argentina l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o 3 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o anh \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Messi v\u00e0 Caballero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/meca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><em>@YahooSportUK:</em></strong> &ldquo;C\u00f3 ai th\u1ea5y Messi \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u00ecm tr\u1ebb l\u1ea1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong><em>&nbsp;</em></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>@RodolfoLanderos: </em></strong>&ldquo;\u0110\u00e0nh r\u1eb1ng Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9? Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00fat c\u00e1 t\u00ednh n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\">Jorge Sampaoli: Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Messi</span><br>\r\nThua th\u1ea3m Croatia, HLV Jorge Sampaoli b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Leo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"433","checkdouble":"189202"},{"date":"04:30 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina trong tr\u1eadn thua Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/Messi-can-lam-gi-de-ngan-Argentina-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.\r\n</h2><h2>Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Argentina t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn thua C\u1ed9ng h\u00f2a S\u00e9c 1-6 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1958.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u1edf h\u1eefu 11 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y Messi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 c\u00fa s\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Trong l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ghi 1 b\u00e0n sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup (n\u0103m 2002).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia 0-3\" title=\"Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/nhung-thong-ke-tham-hai-cua-argentina-trong-tran-thua-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia 0-3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n2 &ndash; T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 pha ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Gonzalo Higuain (1) v\u00e0 Sergio Aguero (1) trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Croatia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 &ndash; Modric l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Croatia ghi b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup, sau Davor Suker v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 &ndash; Croatia th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9, t\u00ednh t\u1ea1i World Cup, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Argentina.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 &ndash; Caballero l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh th\u1ee9 4 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, sau David De Gea, Wojciech Szczesny v\u00e0 Mohammed Al-Owais.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia 0-3 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Caballero ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 trong khung g\u1ed7\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/willy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Caballero ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 trong khung g\u1ed7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n4 &ndash; Luka Modric l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 4 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, sau Cris Ronaldo, Coutinho v\u00e0 Nacho. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb La Liga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">100 &ndash; T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 % c\u1ee7a Luka Modric trong c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi (2/2), t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng (2/2) v\u00e0 th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn (3/3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\">Jorge Sampaoli: Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Messi</span><br>\r\nThua th\u1ea3m Croatia, HLV Jorge Sampaoli b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Leo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-