/div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-argentina-vs-croatia-463-189188.html\">Argentina 0-3 Croatia (KT): Messi m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Albiceleste thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"431","checkdouble":"189204"},{"date":"04:52 22/06","title":"Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/messi-duoc-khuyen-giai-nghe-sau-tran-thua-tham-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i World Cup. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, khi Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nArgentina tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi cho thi\u00ean h\u1ea1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng d\u00f9 Albiceleste ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ebfm ai ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Rebic, Modric v\u00e0 Rakitic \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm Argentina trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia, t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@GaryLineker: </strong></em>&ldquo;M\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Croatia, nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1eebng \u1ea5y n\u0103m theo d\u00f5i \u0110T Argentina thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u00f4i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecd t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/me.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi v\u00e0 Argentina ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<em><strong><br>\r\n@Jermainejunior:</strong></em><strong> </strong>&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i cho Messi, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau Copa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@WelBeast:</strong></em><strong> </strong>&ldquo;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho Sampaoli v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean anh ta \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Iceland. N\u1ebfu qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Argentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<em>&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@katienolan:</strong></em> &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n cho Salah c\u1ee7a Argentina.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@MiguelDelaney: </strong></em>&ldquo;Messi r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Khi b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y quay l\u1ea1i \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Argentina l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o 3 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o anh \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Messi v\u00e0 Caballero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/meca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><em>@YahooSportUK:</em></strong> &ldquo;C\u00f3 ai th\u1ea5y Messi \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u00ecm tr\u1ebb l\u1ea1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong><em>&nbsp;</em></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>@RodolfoLanderos: </em></strong>&ldquo;\u0110\u00e0nh r\u1eb1ng Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9? Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00fat c\u00e1 t\u00ednh n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\">Jorge Sampaoli: Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Messi</span><br>\r\nThua th\u1ea3m Croatia, HLV Jorge Sampaoli b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Leo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"430","checkdouble":"189205"},{"date":"05:09 22/06","title":"\"T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n cho Messi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/tat-ca-chung-ta-deu-cam-thay-buon-cho-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 thua th\u1ea3m Croatia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Zabaleta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi sau tr\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2>Zabaleta cho r\u1eb1ng Messi s\u1ebd t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">El Pulga v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, khi Argentina thua th\u1ea3m Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u xa x\u00f4i nh\u01b0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Pablo Zabaleta, anh cho r\u1eb1ng Lionel Messi s\u1ebd t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia ngay sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Premier League cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc cho Messi, kh\u00f4ng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu Messi t\u1eeb b\u1ecf sau World Cup 2018.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd 4 n\u0103m n\u1eefa m\u1edbi t\u1edbi World Cup 2022 t\u1ea1i Qatar. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Argentina \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn, h\u1ecd r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng mong ch\u1edd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u0103m 2014, sau \u0111\u00f3 thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Copa America.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zabaleta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Argentina sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia\" title=\"messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/tat-ca-chung-ta-deu-cam-thay-buon-cho-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zabaleta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Argentina sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Argentina \u0111ang r\u1ea5t khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y. HLV Sampaoli c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1edbi Argentina, th\u1eadt k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u1ede hi\u1ec7p 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec sau sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Caballero. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Argentina \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd n\u00ean l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd th\u1ea5y Otamendi chuy\u1ec1n h\u1ecfng t\u1ea1i Man City, v\u00e0 Rojo v\u1edbi Man United &ndash; t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Zabaleta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Argentina sau tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u C\u0110V y\u00eau qu\u00fd Albiceleste mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, Argentina s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nigeria v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-duoc-khuyen-giai-nghe-sau-tran-thua-tham-croatia-421-189205.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/messi-duoc-khuyen-giai-nghe-sau-tran-thua-tham-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-duoc-khuyen-giai-nghe-sau-tran-thua-tham-croatia-421-189205.html\">Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m Croatia</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i World Cup. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-argentina-thua-tham-croatia-465-189204.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/17.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-argentina-thua-tham-croatia-465-189204.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Argentina thua th\u1ea3m Croatia</span><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p khi Lionel Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Croatia \u0111\u00e2m cho ba nh\u00e1t ki\u1ebfm t\u1ea1i Nizhny Novgorod.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"429","checkdouble":"189206"},{"date":"06:25 22/06","title":"Argentina \u0111\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1n: Aguero c\u00f4ng khai \"b\u1eadt\" HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/argentina-dai-loai-aguero-cong-khai-bat-hlv-truong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV c\u1ee7a Argentina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sergio Aguero b\u1eadt HLV Sampaoli khi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAguero v\u00f9ng v\u1eb1ng sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u00e0o. Qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Jorge Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i</span> khi cho r\u1eb1ng, Argentina l\u00e0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9 che \u0111i v\u1ea7ng h\u00e0o quang c\u1ee7a Messi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh. El Kun g\u1eaft g\u1ecfng: <strong>\u201c\u00d4ng ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u00f4ng ta mu\u1ed1n.\u201d</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina \u0111\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1n Aguero b\u1eadt HLV Sampaoli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Argentina \u0111\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1n Aguero b\u1eadt HLV Sampaoli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/argentina-dai-loai-aguero-cong-khai-bat-hlv-truong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aguero b\u1eadt HLV Sampaoli sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu Argentina l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cNgay l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cS\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng hy v\u1ecdng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria\u201d \u2013 Aguero cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n ngay ph\u00fat 54, thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng Gonzalo Higuain. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Sergio Aguero l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t trong hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00f2n t\u00ednh trong to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u1eddi gian anh g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man City ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam vi\u1ec7c Aguero b\u1eadt HLV Sampaoli v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Higuain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-duoc-khuyen-giai-nghe-sau-tran-thua-tham-croatia-421-189205.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/messi-duoc-khuyen-giai-nghe-sau-tran-thua-tham-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-duoc-khuyen-giai-nghe-sau-tran-thua-tham-croatia-421-189205.html\">Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m Croatia</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i World Cup. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"428","checkdouble":"189209"},{"date":"06:41 22/06","title":"Perisic: \"Argentina kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/perisic-argentina-khong-phai-mot-doi-bong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1 nh\u1ee5c Albiceleste, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Argentina v\u00e0 Leo Messi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPerisic vui m\u1eebng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng mong ch\u1edd nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-argentina-vs-croatia-463-189188.html\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Argentina</span>. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng oanh li\u1ec7t b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, Lionel Messi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;g\u00e1nh team&rdquo;. Sau tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, khi cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh El Pulga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Messi l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Cristiano Ronaldo&rdquo; &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. Argentina c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed1i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perisic chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Argentina v\u00e0 Messi\" title=\"Perisic chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/perisic-argentina-khong-phai-mot-doi-bong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Argentina v\u00e0 Messi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Croatia, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch n\u0103m 1998. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9. Hi\u1ec7n nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i \u0111ang ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd&rdquo; &ndash; Ivan Perisic chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Argentina, Messi v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Croatia s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Argentina, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o may m\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-duoc-khuyen-giai-nghe-sau-tran-thua-tham-croatia-421-189205.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/messi-duoc-khuyen-giai-nghe-sau-tran-thua-tham-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-duoc-khuyen-giai-nghe-sau-tran-thua-tham-croatia-421-189205.html\">Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m Croatia</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i World Cup. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-hoanh-trang-cua-croatia-421-189200.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"427","checkdouble":"189212"},{"date":"06:54 22/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (22/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2262018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 22/6 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thu