\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); text-align: center;\">22/06 17:00</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); text-align: center;\">22/06 17:00</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">VTV5</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); text-align: center;\">22/06 18:00</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"426","checkdouble":"189216"},{"date":"15:47 21/06","title":"S\u1ed1c: Roy Keane t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n... \"v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u\" tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Ferguson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/soc-roy-keane-tung-muon-vat-dau-tro-ly-hlv-ferguson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u2013 Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRoy Keane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Roy Keane t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. Sau khi r\u1eddi M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169, b\u1edfi anh t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sir Alex &ndash; HLV Carlos Queiroz c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Ferguson v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2002/03, gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i quay l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2004. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Queiroz \u0111ang l\u00e0 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Iran chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 Keane \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c &ldquo;\u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9&rdquo; n\u0103m x\u01b0a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc&rdquo; &ndash; Keane cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Man United. Carlos Queiroz c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u1edfi m\u1edf cho l\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi nghe s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz khi c\u00f2n \u1edf M.U\" title=\"Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/soc-roy-keane-tung-muon-vat-dau-tro-ly-hlv-ferguson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz khi c\u00f2n \u1edf M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean khi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ra \u0111i, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2004, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Queiroz th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tranh c\u00e3i n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y nghi ng\u1edd l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u l\u1ea1i qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u00f4ng \u1ea5y r\u1eddi b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111e d\u1ecda v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Carlos Queiroz l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong vai tr\u00f2 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Ferguson, nh\u01b0ng Carlos Queiroz kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Patrice Evra t\u1eebng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 g\u1ea7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi b\u1ecb Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz, HLV n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2008, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n b\u1ecb tr\u00ed HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. \u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2011, \u00f4ng nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Iran cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189082.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/5/26/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189082.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o t\u1edbi CLB Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh Ruben Loftus-Cheek m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CLB Chelsea v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"425","checkdouble":"189159"},{"date":"15:50 21/06","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p sau World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/lo-dien-hlv-dau-tien-that-nghiep-sau-world-cup-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Hector Cuper c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/Lo-dien-HLV-dau-tien-that-nghiep-sau-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00d4ng Hector Cuper c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p sau World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ai C\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sau 28 n\u0103m, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 62 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, Hector Cuper. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau hai th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1ecb HLV n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ai C\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y VCK World Cup 2018 l\u00e0m \u2018th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o\u2019 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc c\u00f3 n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV Hector Cuper. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n th\u00ec hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd \u2018\u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ai, n\u1ea5y \u0111i\u2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Ai C\u1eadp, hai tr\u1eadn thua v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn HLV Cuper kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y. C\u0169ng theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Ai C\u1eadp, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 HLV Cuper m\u00e0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ban tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n l\u00e3o l\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo ng\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu chia tay Ai C\u1eadp. \"Vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu L\u0110B\u0110 Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ra \u0111i\u201d, HLV Cuper cho hay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi HLV Cuper nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 sau cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia, di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 21h00 ng\u00e0y 25/06, gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-giup-nga-da-bai-ai-cap-tai-world-cup-2018-421-189081.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/3-yeu-to-giup-nga-da-bai-ai-cap-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-giup-nga-da-bai-ai-cap-tai-world-cup-2018-421-189081.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Nga \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nAi C\u1eadp s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba qua Mohamed Salah. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eabn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-salah-tro-lai-nhung-sao-khong-the-loi-hai-nhu-o-liverpool-421-188989.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/goc-nhin-salah-tro-lai-nhung-sao-khong-the-loi-hai-nhu-o-liverpool.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-salah-tro-lai-nhung-sao-khong-the-loi-hai-nhu-o-liverpool-421-188989.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Liverpool?</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, NHM \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf sau khi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/ai-cap-tham-bai-thua-cung-boi-mohamed-salah-466-189027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ai-cap-tham-bai-thua-cung-boi-mohamed-salah.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/ai-cap-tham-bai-thua-cung-boi-mohamed-salah-466-189027.html\">Ai C\u1eadp th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i: Thua c\u0169ng b\u1edfi... Mohamed Salah</span><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y Mohamed Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 kim t\u1ef1 th\u00e1p n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y n\u00ean c\u1ea3 khi ti\u1ec3u Pharaoh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh vai ph\u1ee5 cho show di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN) <o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"424","checkdouble":"189160"},{"date":"16:07 21/06","title":"B\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Lukaku, Hazard n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-soi-dong-cung-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y tr\u00f4i qua, xu th\u1ebf th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5. V\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n- <strong>Australia kh\u00f4ng thua </strong>(+1/2)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>H\u00f2a 0-0 ho\u1eb7c Australia th\u1eafng 1-0</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 21/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>\u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian: </em>19h ng\u00e0y 21/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>Samara Arena (Samara)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>\u0110an M\u1ea1ch -0.87*0:1/2*0.83 Australia<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Nhi\u1ec1u 0.92*2*-0.99 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia (\u00dac) v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia (\u00dac) v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/nhan-dinh-dan-mach-vs-australia-va-nhan-dinh-dan-mach-vs-uc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia 19h ng\u00e0y 21/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi (U 2)</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Yussuf Poulsen. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 truy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i cho Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 pha c\u1ee9u thua, \u0111a ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1u ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSchmeichel t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n 32 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 36 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Anh ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m sau khi c\u00f9ng Leicester v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha Peter Schmeichel v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Schmeichel toa sang tai Dan Mach\" title=\"thu mon Schmeichel toa sang tai Dan Mach\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/thu-mon-Schmeichel-toa-sang-tai-Dan-Mach.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Schmeichel l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a c\u1ee7a \u0110T&nbsp;\u0110an M\u1ea1ch</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Simon Kjaer l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u00e1n s\u1ef1 trong \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp trung \u1edf h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00fap \u0110an M\u1ea1ch r\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh c\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 5 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 trong tay, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Age Hareide c\u00e0ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i thi tri\u1ec3n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia tin l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bong-da-peru-vs-dan-mach-bang-c-463-188649.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/ket-qua-peru-vs-dan-mach-bang-c.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bong-da-peru-vs-dan-mach-bang-c-463-188649.html\">Peru 0-1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch (KT): D\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed3i, chi\u1ebfn binh Inca b\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi tay nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec</span><br>\r\n<span>Thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e9p v\u1ebf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 song Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec l\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee9 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t: b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Peru ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u00e1...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn sang b\u00ean kia, Australia kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thua k\u00e9m \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ef3 l\u1ee3m. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi t\u1eadn ph\u00fat 80 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ecbu thua b\u1edfi b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Aziz Behich. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 d\u00e0i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Australia c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y thua k\u00e9m v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. M\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn gi\u1eb1ng co s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi khan hi\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</strong><br>\r\n- \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 5 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\n- 5 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 4 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: </strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Australia kh\u00f4ng thua (+1/2)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n9 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, Australia ch\u1ec9 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Na Uy. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 8 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 s\u00e1t n\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kho\u1ea3ng 5 ng\u00e0y, Australia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may. 2 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i. C\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR m\u1edbi x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng qua v\u1ea1ch v\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Australia thua dau Phap\" title=\"Australia thua dau Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Australia-thua-dau-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Australia thua \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Phap</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c Australia thua k\u00e9m qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 1-0 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Poulsen ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ebfm hoi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a B\u1eafc \u00c2u t\u1ea1o ra. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Peru v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc Schmeichel m\u1edbi gi\u00fap h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAustralia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 Peru, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</strong><br>\r\n- Australia b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 8/10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n- <strong>Australia kh\u00f4ng thua </strong>(+1/2)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>H\u00f2a 0-0 ho\u1eb7c Australia th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Australia kh\u00f4ng thua qu\u00e1 2 qu\u1ea3 (+2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Australia kh\u00f4ng thua qu\u00e1 1 qu\u1ea3 (+3/4)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 4 qu\u1ea3 (O 4)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 3 (U 3)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 1 (U 1)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"423","checkdouble":"189162"},{"date":"16:21 21/06","title":"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i MU v\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/liverpool-muon-danh-bai-mu-va-tottenham-vu-sao-aston-villa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Jack Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Liverpool-muon-mua-Jack-Grealish-cua-Aston-Villa-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap Aston Villa l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng, song \u0111\u1ec3 thua Fulham.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. MU quan t\u00e2m Jack Grealish, Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Pochettino c\u1ee7a Tottenham c\u0169ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Jack Grealish \u1edf Spurs.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, HLV Klopp \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/liverpool-muon-danh-bai-mu-va-tottenham-vu-sao-aston-villa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Tottenham v\u00e0 MU trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Liverpool ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp r\u1ea5t m\u00e1t tay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Jack Grealish ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf s\u00e2n Anfield.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAston Villa \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 v\u00f4 danh nh\u01b0 Jack Grealish.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Aston Villa \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish, 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Aston Villa nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"422","checkdouble":"189164"},{"date":"16:07 21/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng n\u1ee5 h\u00f4n n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/nhung-nu-hon-nong-bong-tren-khan-dai-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>World Cup 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga xinh \u0111\u1eb9p. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tranh t\u00e0i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i bi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i l\u00e0 n\u01a1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng n\u